            <title>[LU-14315] Increase fsx iteration to improve coverage (particularly fallocate)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14315</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Test-suite sanityn.sh test_16/x is already running 2500 iterations of fsx. To increase coverage particularly for fallocate() call increase iteration from 2500 to 10,000 or thereabouts. This although increases the runtime sightly also greatly increase the coverage for the fsx runs.&lt;/p&gt;

